title: Quiz 6 - Puzzles
instruction:
Directions (21-25): Read the given information carefully and answer the questions given below. 

 

Nine persons Amit, Brijesh, Chetan, Deepak, Eshan, Farooq, Gautam, Harpreet, and Inderjeet are born in nine different year viz. 1976, 1978, 1980, 1984, 1988, 1991, 1995, 2001, 2004 but not necessarily in the same order. The age of persons will be calculated with respect to the year 2021. They all have different occupations viz. Architect, Professor, Singer, Painter, Dancer, Home-keeper, Banker, Doctor, and engineer but not necessarily in the same order.

Farooq is younger than Gautam but older than Harpreet, who is not a home-keeper. The one whose age is 41 years is not a dancer. The sum of age of the professor and Chetan is 62 years. Only three persons are younger to Brijesh, who is an Architect. The one who is the second oldest is a singer. Deepakâ€™s age is not 26 years. Eshan was born in a year after Brijesh, but he was not born in a leap year. Only two persons was born between Eshan and Amit. The sum of age of Deepak and the one who is Doctor is 67 years. The difference between the age of home-keeper and the singer is 6 years. Amit is not a home-keeper. Inderjeet was not born in 1984 and he is neither a professor nor a singer. Deepak is neither an engineer nor a banker. The sum of age of Painter and Dancer is 61 years. Amit is not an engineer.
